      • getParameters

        Map<String,Boolean> getParameters()
        Returns the input parameters that this artifact uses. Implementations must include ManagedArtifact.ARTIFACT_FILE_NAME
        Returns:
        the input parameters as a Map of String, Boolean where the string is the parameter name, and the boolean states if it is a required parameter.
